Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我這種小人物糾纏合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態似乎愈發嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少看不起我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也能應付嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就借你點…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要控制…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的…控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是九尾化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險 抓緊去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…如果不制止那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 請交給我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我雖然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但曾經也是村子的守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護這裡…保護巨坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑哥哥現在的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能抵達目的地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…帶我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法茲 不可以再挑食了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算難吃也不能挑肥揀瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要增強體力 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德 你最大 要振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有困難要互相幫助哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 要好好照顧大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照看好米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後或許會經歷很多酸甜苦辣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做大家的支柱哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時扇了你一記耳光 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有米娜察覺到鳴人哥哥的異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能理解你…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後也許會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不要逃避 堅強起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥還有大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是短暫的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和大家在一起真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是相當幸福的時光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 孩子們就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能死裡逃生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那無論如何都要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是音律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據那傢伙說是按特定順序排列的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的順序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是米娜哼得曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很早前就一直哼著的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬盡 殺絕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 完全失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 好像脫臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 快幫我治療
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 可是九尾的力量太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能束縛它多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 得趕緊想其他辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我決不會放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來 還是趕緊讓天之矛停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再次看著最愛之人落下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直 一直都喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拼命抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我再也不會放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放手的話 還不如一起掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是從那時起對你念念不忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我比你高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你變禿 變胖 變得遲鈍 變得懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你對我敬而遠之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我還是一直喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 誰去保護那些孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子的未來只有靠你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守護 想要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的人們 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助爸爸和媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信著 相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信正義的力量 相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護好那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛著你…愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 趕緊阻止那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少搗亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救我一命 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 真的感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,竟然用穢土轉生讓人柱力們復活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我決饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這場戰爭由我來阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鳴人能夠感知敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這樣他就必須得出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,果然不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,今日起 千手的火之意志將要消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鳴人 參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,終於輪到我出場了
